<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pale-adj">pale <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /peɪl/    美 /peɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(颜色) 淡的；浅的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He wore a pale blue tie. 
他戴着一条淡蓝色的领带。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(光线) 暗淡的；微弱的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a pale moon 
朦胧的月色</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>苍白的；灰白的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He looks pale from his long illness. 
他因长期生病而脸色苍白。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On hearing the news of the school shooting, she <strong>went / turned pale.</strong>
听到校园枪击事件的消息，她脸色苍白。</p></div></div>